text: haey puok del ban ksang mea sche t daembi bangk krohthnak ( dl anak mean chomnue) ning noam aoy kmean chomnue haeyning bangk pheap bek bak rveang banda anak del mean chomnue promteang triem samreab chn na del ban thveusangkream brachheang nung a l laoh ning anakneasar robsa trong tangpi moun mk . haey puokke brakadchea nung sbath tha yeung min chngban avei krawpi phl la( karsaangosang mea sche t nih) laey . haey a l laoh chea anak thveusaeaksaei tha pitabrakd nasa puokke chea puok del phout kohk
